---
title: Sri Lankan Prawn Pilaf with Beetroot & Herb Slaw
description: 'The Pearl of the Indian Ocean' - that's the name given to Sri Lanka by visitors inspired by the island's beauty. We think its food is worth waxing lyrical about too!  Sri Lankans love both spice and seafood so we're celebrating those two things here and adding some super-seasonal beetroot on the side. Enjoy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sri-lankan-prawn-pilaf-wk34-93ba327a-3f5b345a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/sri-lankan-prawn-pilaf-wk34-595524ef4f78db392439ac82-28c5b28e.pdf
course: main course
time required: 40 minutes
